{"tid":2117810,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［年經］ 2020 JS3624 埋土職業治療討論區","createTime":"2020-07-21T05:54:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-13T01:32:44.000Z","uid":231099,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"e85e677c0c0f17ab1d4489aafb97303046b94955","tid":2117810,"uid":231099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T05:54:12.000Z","msg":"聽日就放榜喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有咩關於職業治療嘅問題都可以喺度問 任問唔嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後想同2020DSEers講聲辛苦曬 你哋好叻好堅強啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />預祝大家聽日[red]放榜<span class=\"x-large\"></span>成功[red]<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d0f684e302220bafea23114781b433d0a71de80","tid":2117810,"uid":358233,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T06:02:42.000Z","msg":"除左多啲心理嘢， 同物理治療有乜分别。"},{"pid":"3b845c8c1247aa413d5dc5d2a29449eb3b2811bb","tid":2117810,"uid":231099,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d0f684e302220bafea23114781b433d0a71de80","tid":2117810,"uid":358233,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T06:02:42.000Z","msg":"除左多啲心理嘢， 同物理治療有乜分别。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T06:28:33.000Z","msg":"問得非常之好啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nOT呢 最主要就係透過活動去維持、改善同埋提升一個人喺生活各個範疇嘅能力，唔同範疇包括工作、學習、自理等等<br />\nOT會提供訓練、教client adaptive techniques又或者畀啲assistive aids client,從而提升client嘅功能同能力，令client有翻信心同能力自己去做翻生活中唔同範疇嘅tasks，去維持佢地嘅尊嚴同生活質素<br />\n<br />\n而PT呢，主要就係靠物理嘅媒介、療法例如電療、水療去改善同提升翻client嘅能力，改善client生活質素<br />\n詳細嘅都係要問翻pt巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://youtu.be/TkHzR4rFMOo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FTkHzR4rFMOo&d=bKbBxrmwQkzC5eAvTqWhP7PGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=4d04d368\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://youtu.be/TkHzR4rFMOo</a><br />\n可以睇下呢條片啊！睇完會清楚多啲OT係做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"077ed18d0d2c1e2bc72fa4d93e8509088759cbb1","tid":2117810,"uid":215774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T06:53:21.000Z","msg":"無讀bio phy會唔會讀唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89bbfcb436fdf1172267bea369c0f8d8c6bb2538","tid":2117810,"uid":231099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"077ed18d0d2c1e2bc72fa4d93e8509088759cbb1","tid":2117810,"uid":215774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T06:53:21.000Z","msg":"無讀bio phy會唔會讀唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T07:24:45.000Z","msg":"唔會唔會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n身邊有啲同學都無讀bio同phy，甚至有啲係文科生，但gpa出到嚟仲高過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以唔驚！year1嘅課程絕對有時間畀大家追翻，只要俾啲掙扎就無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7b1ca922d52bc65a222382caae22d560580777f","tid":2117810,"uid":303372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T12:11:52.000Z","msg":"ot jj 留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d5542f11762dcce73dce54d0511b5eecc980703","tid":2117810,"uid":154328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T12:17:21.000Z","msg":"PT OT<br />\n邊樣工作上冇咁辛苦hea啲<br />\n通常放工收幾點"},{"pid":"7a64805ff36d790e43a5664416e9ab6d1a30a316","tid":2117810,"uid":146887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T23:46:06.000Z","msg":"自修生搶閘派grade了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想問下4564 656<br />\nelective係 phy chem m2<br />\n係咪唔夠讀ot 㩒完weighting好似係28x<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7fa590929456d6aff3bf8962c1cd4bcbc1a23f0","tid":2117810,"uid":36014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"re